<h2>1. Exhibit Index</h2>
<p>
Each artifact below is identified by a SHA-256 hash computed over the exact
bytes of the file produced for this case. A reviewer can recompute the hash of
any exhibit introduced into evidence and confirm it is byte-identical to the
file produced here. Hashing algorithm: SHA-256 (FIPS 180-4).
</p>
